text: Everyone who is the oldest sibling.
Everyone who is the youngest sibling.
Everyone who is a middle child.
Everyone who is an only child.
Everyone who talks to a family member every day.
Everyone who has a big extended family.
Everyone who has moved far away from their family.
Everyone who has a family tradition they love.
Everyone who looks more like their mom than their dad (or vice versa).
Everyone who is an aunt or uncle.
